OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1781718498
OL,3,CCouncil told it requires improvement
OL,4,Cafter adult social care review
OL,6,FA report into adult social care
OL,7,Fprovisions at Southampton City Council
OL,8,Fhas found the authority requires
OL,9,Fimprovement.
OL,11,FThe Care Quality Commission (CQC) said
OL,12,F"significant and prolonged leadership
OL,13,Finstability had affected its ability
OL,14,Fto deliver consistently good access to
OL,15,Fadult social care".
OL,17,FBut it also praised "good examples of
OL,18,Fteams working well together and
OL,19,Ffinding new ways to improve care".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
