FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1781718498
OL,3,CCouncil told it requires improvement
OL,4,Cafter adult social care review
OL,6,FThe council has apologised to affected
OL,7,Fresidents, adding it has already taken
OL,8,F"decisive" action to address the
OL,9,Fissues that were raised in the report.
OL,11,FThe CQC investigated nine areas -
OL,12,Fincluding safeguarding and assessments
OL,13,F- to determine how the council is
OL,14,Fmeeting its responsibilities.
OL,16,FOn a scale of one to four - where one
OL,17,Fis the lowest and four the highest
OL,18,Fpossible scores - it gave the
OL,19,Fauthority a mark of one in some areas.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1781718498
OL,3,CCouncil told it requires improvement
OL,4,Cafter adult social care review
OL,6,FThe body says it has written to the
OL,7,Fhealth secretary, outlining where
OL,8,Fimprovements are needed.
OL,10,FIt's chief inspector of adult social
OL,11,Fcare and integrated care stated that,
OL,12,Fbecause the council had been through
OL,13,F11 directors of adult social services
OL,14,Fin the the previous 12 years, its
OL,15,Fcurrent leaders "didn't yet have a
OL,16,Fgrip on the areas of concern in order
OL,17,Fto address them quickly".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
