CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1781718498
OL,3,CCouncil told it requires improvement
OL,4,Cafter adult social care review
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"We found this reflected in serious
OL,12,Fconcerns about safeguarding
OL,13,Fprocesses," they added.
OL,15,FThe council was told it needs to
OL,16,Fprovide better respite support for
OL,17,Funpaid carers and improve how quickly
OL,18,Fit carries out reviews of care
OL,19,Fpackages, in the report's
OL,20,Frecommendations.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
