OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1781718498
OL,3,CCouncil told it requires improvement
OL,4,Cafter adult social care review
OL,6,FA failure to appoint a strategic
OL,7,Fsafeguarding lead for a "significant
OL,8,Fperiod" had also left services
OL,9,F"without proper direction", the report
OL,10,Ffound.
OL,12,FBut it also praised some areas,
OL,13,Fcommenting that leaders had "responded
OL,14,Feffectively" to replace a partner
OL,15,Fcompany, that provided equipment to
OL,16,Fhelp people remain independent at
OL,17,Fhome, when it ceased trading.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
