PN,38706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1781718498
OL,3,CCouncil told it requires improvement
OL,4,Cafter adult social care review
OL,6,FIt also "acted quickly on complaints
OL,7,Fabout disability-related expenses by
OL,8,Freviewing and changing its processes
OL,9,Fafter five complaints, resulting in no
OL,10,Ffurther complaints of that type".
OL,12,FIn a statement, Southampton City
OL,13,FCouncil said that, since the
OL,14,Finspection, it has taken decisions to
OL,15,F"accelerate improvements".
OL,17,FCouncillor Christian Cox, Cabinet
OL,18,FMember for Adult Social Care and
OL,19,FPublic Health, said: "Many people
OL,20,Freceive good support, but it must be
OL,21,Fconsistently high-quality for everyone.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
